org.apache.hcatalog.data.transfer
Class HCatReader

Object
  HCatReader
Direct Known Subclasses:
HCatInputFormatReader
public abstract class HCatReader
extends Object

This abstract class is internal to HCatalog and abstracts away the notion of underlying system from which reads will be done.
